arm_annotation:
Generic trap porting note:
x86 traps use segment/privilege checks; ARM64 uses EL (Exception Levels).
Preserve logic: Return to guest via ERET on ARM (vs IRET on x86).
Memory: ARM64 is weakly ordered; add barriers (DSB/ISB) around trap entry/exit.
